('business:1-1-role-of-business-enterprise:match:4f606247', 'business', 'business:1-1-role-of-business-enterprise', '1.1 Role of Business Enterprise', 'match', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Which definition matches the key term “Creativity”?", "options": ["The characteristic of not giving up when difficulties arise — working hard to overcome problems.", "The ability to think of new ideas, design original products, or solve problems in innovative ways.", "Believing strongly in your own ability to succeed and inspiring that belief in others.", "Being prepared to put personal money, time, or reputation into a business venture that may fail."]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 1, "explain": "“Creativity” means: The ability to think of new ideas, design original products, or solve problems in innovative ways."}'::jsonb),
